# Testing Rules

## Cấu trúc

```
tests/
├── unit/              # Fast, no external deps
│   ├── test_*.py      # Đặt tên match module testing
│   └── conftest.py    # Shared fixtures
├── integration/       # Real services (DB, API, Tailscale)
│   ├── test_*.py
│   └── conftest.py
└── fixtures/          # Sample data files
    └── *.yaml/.json
```

## Naming convention

- File: `test_<module>.py` (vd `test_provider_router.py` cho `pio_lab/providers/router.py`)
- Function: `test_<scenario>` mô tả đặc tính cụ thể
- Class (optional): `TestClassName` cho group related tests

## Pytest conventions

```python
import pytest
from unittest.mock import AsyncMock, patch


@pytest.mark.asyncio
async def test_router_calls_first_provider_in_chain():
    """Router phải thử provider đầu trong chain trước khi fallback."""
    # Given
    router = ProviderRouter(config_path=test_config)
    router.load()

    # When
    with patch.object(router, "_call_provider", new=AsyncMock(return_value=mock_response)):
        result = await router.call("test.key", messages=[...])

    # Then
    assert result["provider"] == "claude"  # provider đầu trong chain
```

## Async tests

- Dùng `@pytest.mark.asyncio` (config trong `pyproject.toml::asyncio_mode = "auto"` cũng OK)
- Mock async với `AsyncMock`, không `Mock`

## Mocking LLM

```python
mock_response = {
    "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "mocked answer"}],
    "stop_reason": "end_turn",
    "usage": {"input_tokens": 10, "output_tokens": 5},
    "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
    "provider": "claude",
    "raw": None,
}

with patch("pio_lab.providers.router.ProviderRouter.call",
           new=AsyncMock(return_value=mock_response)):
    # Test code
```

## Fixtures

```python
# conftest.py
@pytest.fixture
async def db_session():
    """Async DB session, auto rollback after test."""
    async with async_session() as s:
        yield s
        await s.rollback()


@pytest.fixture
def sample_task():
    return {"input": "Test request", "metadata": {}}
```

## Markers

- `@pytest.mark.unit` (default — không cần mark)
- `@pytest.mark.integration` — cần real services
- `@pytest.mark.slow` — > 5s
- `@pytest.mark.skip(reason="...")` — tạm skip
- `@pytest.mark.xfail` — known failure (chưa fix)

## Coverage targets

| Package | Min coverage |
|---|---|
| `pio_lab/core/` | 80% |
| `pio_lab/providers/` | 75% |
| `pio_lab/layer3_chief_of_staff/` | 75% |
| `pio_lab/layer4_departments/` | 60% |
| `pio_lab/security/` | 90% |
| Other layers | 60% |

Run với coverage:
```bash
pytest --cov=pio_lab --cov-report=html
open htmlcov/index.html
```

## Đừng

- ❌ KHÔNG mock everything — integration test cần real services
- ❌ KHÔNG test private methods (`_helper`) trực tiếp — test qua public
- ❌ KHÔNG dùng real API key trong unit test
- ❌ KHÔNG depend test order — mỗi test độc lập
- ❌ KHÔNG commit fixtures với real secrets

## Khi viết test cho 1 milestone

1. Đọc `@CODEX_HANDOFF.md` section M{N} → acceptance criteria
2. Mỗi acceptance criterion → ít nhất 1 test
3. Edge case: 1-2 test thêm
4. Error path: 1 test cho mỗi exception type
5. Run: `pytest tests/unit/test_<milestone>.py -v`

## Smoke test sau milestone done

- Chạy 1 scenario từ `@docs/EXAMPLES.md` tương ứng
- Vd M3 done → run scenario 1 (Q&A đơn giản)
